{"data": {"__GLOBAL": {"_ATTACH_BASE_VIEW": "img.nga.178.com/attachments"}, "__U": {"150058": {"uid": 150058, "username": "UID:150058", "credit": 135537218, "medal": "272,207,157,92", "reputation": "28_30,61_0,147_775,130_10", "groupid": -1, "memberid": 73, "avatar": null, "yz": 4, "site": null, "honor": null, "regdate": 1123989606, "mute_time": null, "postnum": 41261, "rvrc": 29, "money": 90765, "thisvisit": 1782893637, "signature": null, "nickname": null, "bit_data": 135537218, "buffs": {"131": [[1618226, 131, 20698560, 150058, 1782779225, 1783038425, 7, 0]]}}, "66989363": {"uid": 66989363, "username": "UID:66989363", "credit": 135275008, "medal": null, "reputation": "147_-300", "groupid": -1, "memberid": 39, "avatar": null, "yz": 4, "site": null, "honor": null, "regdate": 1762774156, "mute_time": null, "postnum": 2756, "rvrc": 10, "money": 0, "thisvisit": 1782868778, "signature": null, "nickname": null, "bit_data": 135275008}, "__GROUPS": {"73": ["学徒", 360672, 73], "39": ["学徒", 98528, 39]}, "__MEDALS": {"272": ["272.gif", "棒棒糖", "叔叔请你吃棒棒糖", 272], "207": ["207.gif", "爆竹声中旧岁除", "一支红杏出墙来", 207], "157": ["157.gif", "王者之剑", "王者之剑活动纪念", 157], "92": ["92.gif", "小心死亡之翼-", "2011年大灾变开服纪念", 92]}, "__REPUTATIONS": {"147": {"150058": 775, "66989363": -300, "0": "大时代"}}}, "__R": [{"pid": 872542171, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 222, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-22 15:00", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "今天哪怕你真的无敌到卖在半导体早上最高点<br/>接回来的点位呢 能有多少差价？<br/>大部分甚至可能是认错买回的<br/>有啥意思<br/>一旦这种模式形成<br/>不管是4浪还是下跌一浪<br/>第一个套的就是这种人。<br/>因为这些人已经习惯了卖了马上就要买回来。", "lou": 3380, "content_length": 201, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1782111635}, {"pid": 872543799, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 147, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-22 15:12", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=872543177,45974302,7786]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=61395264]村上吹树[/uid] (2026-06-22 15:08):[/b]<br/><br/>早上他们问我做不做T，我说高手可以做…但我不是高手。[s:ac:计划通][/quote]<br/>很多自认为高手的 死的不是追高 也不是逃顶<br/><br/>是自以为是的抄底<br/><br/>而抄底这种概念 是不断的在上涨过程中被驯化出来的<br/><br/><br/>------------我记得这个概念我之前说过一摸一样的话。", "lou": 3381, "content_length": 155, "reply_to": 872543177, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1782112361}, {"pid": 872582315, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 300, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-22 21:40", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "熬过了下跌通道没亏钱 然后能在基本最低位满仓 <br/>然后现在还在担心市场？<br/>现在慌的不是踏空的人吗？<br/>你们都是些什么心态啊", "lou": 3382, "content_length": 108, "14": {"17": 1}, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1782135635}, {"pid": 872612824, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 87, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-23 09:21", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "还没开盘 液冷就下班了", "lou": 3383, "content_length": 20, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1782177670}, {"pid": 872620706, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 111, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-23 10:17", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "金属类被批量结账<br/>炒那些元素周期表的要收肉了", "lou": 3384, "content_length": 42, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1782181035}, {"pid": 872621044, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 73, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-23 10:19", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=872620892,45974302,7828]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=65664557]维拉帕米不是米[/uid] (2026-06-23 10:18):[/b]<br/><br/>稀土也算在内对吧狼大[/quote]<br/>嗯  我这些方向 稀土小金属我都剩个利润  暂时不做了  留个利润<br/>我目前着重新能源方向。", "lou": 3385, "content_length": 79, "reply_to": 872620892, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1782181167}, {"pid": 872621886, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 140, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-23 10:25", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "新能源方向<br/>锂矿 锂电 光伏 电网<br/>因为小作文太多 <br/>我目前只关注电池和电网。<br/><br/>主要是科技那边我也不动了  所以赚了的减出来的钱只能去新能源。<br/>科技那边我一分不加。", "lou": 3386, "content_length": 142, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1782181504}, {"pid": 872625904, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 87, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-23 10:51", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "半导体已经开始有杂毛起来了  踏空资金还是太多了。", "lou": 3387, "content_length": 46, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1782183109}, {"pid": 872626796, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 105, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-23 10:57", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "我和你们不一样啊 <br/>我做滚动的<br/>之前我分享过 我很多票会在特定位置减仓 加仓<br/>现在减出来的都是大涨的 小金属 科技类<br/>那减出来的我不可能回科技了 所以我肯定找另外一个我认为不弱于科技的方向去做。<br/><br/>你们可以问问小图 他最近在哪里发财就懂了。", "lou": 3388, "content_length": 214, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1782183437}, {"pid": 872628227, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 74, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-23 11:06", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=872627677,45974302,7841]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=65490615]子午卯酉甲乙丙丁[/uid] (2026-06-23 11:03):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大，之前不是4000以上不会换主线么。目前这些板块是找的低位补涨的吧？[/quote]<br/>我没有看空主线啊 我就是不追高 去做中报行情而已。", "lou": 3389, "content_length": 51, "reply_to": 872627677, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1782183999}, {"pid": 872641340, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 118, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-23 12:43", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=872637352,45974302,7851]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=65247842]几脏[/uid] (2026-06-23 12:08):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大，广西长线运河票还是拿到通航？[/quote]<br/>哈 哈哈?啊哈？", "lou": 3390, "content_length": 18, "reply_to": 872637352, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1782189836}, {"pid": 872641712, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 154, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-23 12:47", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "这里最难受的一个是低位清盘超跌股 然后出场不回来的<br/>一个是最近几天开始追高来买科技的<br/>为什么呢 因为他们不知道自己买的科技是什么 高位来找逻辑，也没有之前的目标价，对应小剧场 -----我买的科技为什么不涨？<br/><br/>我能提前预判的都给你们预判了<br/>科技最好的右侧买点已经过了 更别说左侧买点了。<br/>这个时候你们还在里面的 也不敢去别的地方的 就等结账就行了 。<br/>结账的方式我之前也给你们分析过了。<br/><br/>我真的 之前都预判完了 现在市场就这么反应了 你们就忘记了我之前说的 还在那问问问问。重复的问。", "lou": 3391, "content_length": 441, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1782190073}, {"pid": 872642355, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 84, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-23 12:54", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "现在科技资金在做什么  在培养你们的习惯呢<br/>培养那些加速进场带杠杆的资金 培养他们每次抄底都能V起来的习惯<br/>你们看过“培养一个好习惯需要几天 ”吗？", "lou": 3392, "content_length": 135, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1782190496}, {"pid": 872642886, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 96, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-23 13:00", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "特别是最后 半导体上游这些元素周期表的  甚至今天到了钒酸钇 碲化锑这种  你们认识吗？我都不认识<br/>从MLCC开始 机构就不断的用小作文轰这个方向<br/>这里没有基本面逻辑的。吃到也就行了。", "lou": 3393, "content_length": 162, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1782190841}, {"pid": 872643125, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 80, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-23 13:03", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=872642894,45974302,7855]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=66222094]kk77咪[/uid] (2026-06-23 13:00):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大，小图让我们来问问你最近在哪发财[/quote]<br/>他不是在电池么 你猜他逻辑哪来的就行了。", "lou": 3394, "content_length": 43, "reply_to": 872642894, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1782191005}, {"pid": 872646643, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 152, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-23 13:42", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "日D附近  今天极限最多4121应该差不多了。", "lou": 3395, "content_length": 37, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1782193365}, {"pid": 872648698, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 67, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-23 14:01", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "科技反倒没怎么跌了。倒是有色那边还在出货。确实是短时间涨太多了", "lou": 3396, "content_length": 62, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1782194519}, {"pid": 872649399, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 76, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-23 14:08", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "有色稀土小金属那边触发集体止损了  指数有点兜不住啊<br/>科技止跌也没用", "lou": 3397, "content_length": 62, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1782194891}, {"pid": 872650083, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 165, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-23 14:13", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "。。。半导体设备又没有比昨天低 也不知道在犬吠什么", "lou": 3398, "content_length": 48, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1782195238}, {"pid": 872651881, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 120, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-23 14:29", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "昨天进来的增量今天都在树上了 不懂几天能救出来", "lou": 3399, "content_length": 44, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1782196140}], "__T": {"fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "topic_misc": null, "subject": "自立自强，科学技术打头阵", "locked": 0, "recommend": 0, "quote_to": null, "quote_from": 0, "type": 36, "replies": 172949, "authorid": 150058, "postdate": 1768179906, "lastpost": 1782914706, "jdata": null, "author": "-阿狼-", "lastposter": "rlshjsi", "digest": 0, "lastmodify": 1782914759, "tpid": 0, "post_misc_var": {"content_length": 412, "fid": 706, "comment_id": ",854270755,860174433", "14": {"17": 1, "14": 6, "13": 4, "12": 1}, "16": "63335896,19412700,26652007,67067074,20672033,66881586,67068843,66199622,60819388,60409766,67057614,60264